Exit Statuses :--

0 - Success # buDefault at the end of the script status code is 0
echo $? - to print out the status code
use case - when you want to use branching operation OR you want to terminate the process if their any error in the script

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
bin $ cat pexit.py
#!/usr/local/bin/python

import sys

print("Something")
sys.exit(0)
print("After exit")
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Output -
bin $ ./pexit.py
Something
bin $ echo $?
0
